{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "防卫战～日出之国宝藏传说！～ 偷懒鼠的黄金梦",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "光秀告诉家康编造宝藏传说\\n是为了给自己打造一片偷懒净土，\\n其实却是为了振兴贫困的村子。\\n察觉到这一切的家康却认为洞穴\\n确实与自己的先祖有关，便继续挖掘。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "你是说我把黄金雕像\\n埋到了洞穴里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不只是雕像，我们至今为止\\n挖到的碗、工具还有木片都是。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "虽然看起来很老旧，\\n实际上却都是近年的东西。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "毕竟这世上可是\\n有着能让东西看起来\\n上年代的做旧手艺啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "既然是做旧的，自然不太可能\\n一开始就埋在那下面吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "所以你们的意思是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "至今为止在洞穴里找到的\\n所有线索都是我造假的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "这怎么可能嘛。\\n首先，我为什么要去做那些\\n造假然后埋进洞里的麻烦事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "确实不太像是你会做的事。\\n但如果是你拜托它们去做的呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "昨天晚上它们\\n打算埋下新的“线索”时\\n被我逮了个正着。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "我确实和小波关系好，\\n但我可没法指挥老鼠啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "就算你不行，你的契约龙\\n大黑天不见得办不到吧。\\n毕竟我都能和小猪崽们交流。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不然我们把能跟动物交流的\\n梅莉贝尔或者乌尔嘉叫来，\\n问问老鼠们到底是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "水井上的家纹也被证实\\n是最近才刻上去的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "光秀，差不多该说实话了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "哎呀……\\n我还以为会再顺利些呢～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那我们从洞穴里挖出的东西\\n果然都是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "没错，都是我为了\\n“天岩户计划”而准备好的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "“天岩户计划”？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "呵呵呵，“天岩户计划”就是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "为我打造一片\\n偷懒净土的计划！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04",
                "100006_08",
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "当初在这村附近看到那口枯井时\\n就在想“要是能一直住在井底\\n不用干活该多好”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "要闭门不出的话，躲井里不是更好？\\n这样就不会被任何人打扰了。\\n不过，我自己又懒得去挖。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "所以我听了水金村的宝藏传说\\n就灵机一动，想起了家康氏族中\\n流传的“狐狸”的故事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "要是能把这两个故事联系起来，\\n家康一定会为了寻找宝藏\\n而帮我在井底挖洞吧～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "所以才在水井上\\n刻了家康的家纹，\\n把我们叫来这里吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "不过帝国军和兰扎卜他们\\n倒是在我的预想之外。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "那些造假的线索\\n也是为了让你们\\n有挖洞的动力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "毕竟要是什么都挖不出来，\\n在挖到合适的深度前\\n你们可能就会放弃了呢～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "只是因为想躲到井里\\n而欺骗我们……\\n你是认真的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "当然是认真的，\\n能用的手段就要用。\\n毕竟我可是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "只想偷懒\\n不被任何人打扰呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哈……我都已经懒得生气了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "帮我挖洞的事，\\n我会补偿你们的。\\n所以这件事可以就此打住吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "大可不必。\\n我们是为了寻求浪漫才来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "从你那里拿挖洞的工钱\\n也感觉怪怪的。\\n各位，我们回去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "没能按计划行事吗。\\n不过，算了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "光秀，我有话要跟你说。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "你们还没回去啊。\\n不是还让山茶花他们帮忙\\n做日出之国的工作吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我觉得返回日出之国之前\\n要先从你这里问出真相。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "真相？我已经都招了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我不这么认为。\\n毕竟你做事一定也会为\\n自己以外之人的利益考虑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "我可没那种闲情雅致。\\n那你又是怎么想的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "此次风波之中受益最大的，\\n当属水金村的村民们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我们寻宝一事\\n让宝藏的传说迅速传开，\\n进而吸引大批游客前来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "而且他们也不可能\\n不知道水井的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "如果你是为了帮他们振兴村子，\\n那一切便都说得通了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "所以，宝藏传说本身其实\\n也是你和村民们为了振兴村子\\n而编出来的谎言对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "然而仅仅是传说的话，并不会\\n吸引太多人。但若是有人真的在\\n这里寻宝，那可信度便会大大提升。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "于是你便利用“狐狸”的故事\\n引诱我来这里寻找宝藏。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "之所以没向兰扎卜他们道出真相，\\n是为了不让村民们受到牵连，\\n我说的没错吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "唉……\\n竟然都被你看穿了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "一切都如家康所说吗。\\n为什么要帮他们编造谎言？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "也算是为了报答他们\\n对我的款待。你们也看到\\n水金村那破败的景象了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "渔业不景气，新开发的旅游业\\n也不顺利。这样下去村子迟早会荒废，\\n我不想看到这一切发生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "啊，不过我想要一个洞\\n躲进去倒是实话。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "把你牵扯进来\\n是我一个人的主意，\\n能别怪罪村民们吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我理解他们\\n为了生存都很拼命，\\n所以自然不会怪罪他们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我也不怪罪帮助他们的你。\\n不过……有些不甘就是了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "你还是那个老好人啊。\\n明明我的确是骗了你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "可你给人添麻烦的时候\\n不也看人吗。我觉得你之所以选我，\\n正是因为你信赖我，把我视作友人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "唉……只要跟你一起，\\n就总会被你牵着鼻子走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "话说那宝藏传说，\\n究竟有几分真几分假？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "嗯？不全是编出来的谎言吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "彻头彻尾的谎言\\n是很难让人信服的。\\n我觉得那传说应该有原型。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "你说得没错。\\n有孩子看到武士把黄金埋到\\n井里的故事的确是我编出来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "但除此以外的所有内容\\n都确实在这个村子流传已久，\\n包括那首童谣。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "身披八目的武士呀，\\n卖力地挖井咿呀喂。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "若是发现了宝藏呢，\\n鬼门关也留不住……吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "而且你在井底发现的那个洞穴\\n也确实是很久以前就有的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "不过要是让你太顺利地发现\\n就没意思了，所以拜托\\n村长他们把入口给埋了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "所以漂流而来的武士\\n挖了井的故事可能是真的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "嗯。而且我认为那武士的\\n真实身份就是“狐狸”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "不不不，那只是我为了引你来\\n而强行关联到一起的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "那么在洞穴里发现的\\n“八猪目”印笼也是你准备的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "那是什么东西？\\n我可没听说过。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "当初发现的时候因为太激动\\n就忘了告诉你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "但是让马蒂殿下鉴定之后，\\n却发现只有那印笼的的确确\\n有100年以上的历史。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "如果那不是\\n光秀准备的东西……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "也许洞穴深处\\n真的埋藏着历史的真相。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_04_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}